{"tid":757340,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[被背叛的痛有誰懂]有無人唔再夠膽深信其他人","createTime":"2018-07-26T18:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T21:41:23.000Z","uid":153493,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dc71e84eeaa940f76eb63ef7055fe5d8f4362bd9","tid":757340,"uid":153493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T18:10:48.000Z","msg":"有無人同我一樣<br />\n成日都太在意人地點諗點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好驚對方唔開心<br />\n但同時委屈左自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n姐係做咩都好諗左人先<br />\n永遠做傻仔比人利用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己親身經歷係帽左<br />\n都可以傻撚到同個狗公講道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望佢好好對隻臭雞唔好令佢得唔到幸福<br />\n但結果其實你想佢個日早d黎嘅臭雞前度<br />\n到最後都係再帽番人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時候再諗番都會好傷好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想其他人開開心心<br />\n但永遠被人當傻仔咁利用同取笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為回憶番當時前度喊撚哂口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係度話估唔到自己其實會鐘意第個<br />\n再被人踢爆左出軌嘅事實<br />\n繼而帽左我呢個男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得自己好錯好天真好傻女<br />\n<br />\n然而好大機會係利用演技假喊<br />\n黎換取我嘅同情心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事實上係唔想搞大佢<br />\n被共同朋友指責係臭雞八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知呢度多唔多00後同我一樣<br />\n好撚易比人利用感情<br />\n永遠都做受害者 <br />\n鐘意自虐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n永遠無乜方法或者行為令人對自己有所畏懼<br />\n<br />\n利申:90後<br />\n你地班00後死mk死番上深圳食海底撈啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真心毒撚怕事永遠都係FF可以還拖反擊<br />\n敢怒不敢言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n怕不論咩情都好<br />\n令一段關係大受影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n純粹9up分享下<br />\n睇下有無巴絲有類似嘅性格或故事分享抒發下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991a60437ab64b54294dad6df9609800ab64d766","tid":757340,"uid":5169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T21:07:45.000Z","msg":"同樓住你差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0f9189632d8dff3e93f4493c814f057949d66e","tid":757340,"uid":176040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T21:22:04.000Z","msg":"same"},{"pid":"6efa5cea5af3ba6049f90aa7e0148c3e9648153e","tid":757340,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T21:39:04.000Z","msg":"從來最信只有自己 <br />\n所有人都會有保留(除家人)"},{"pid":"b1815b72f63acff458627ddcbda9915338c9f106","tid":757340,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T21:41:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}